data.description: This is a great 6th floor Seacrest condo, PRICED TO SELL, and ready for a new homeowner! Recently updated with freshly painted walls and NEW flooring! One covered parking slot is included. This Seacrest Condo complex has a great beach access, amenities including a work out facility and an indoor/outdoor pool. Conveniently located to shopping, local artisan's, eateries and a short drive to activities in Destin. A MUST SEE in person to appreciate the close proximity to the beautiful Northwest Florida beaches and views! Buyer to verify all data, details and information important to them.
data.whatILove: Was our dream family vacation. Very close to the gulf of Mexico, plenty of restaurants and activities as well. Great location to enjoy yourself.
